  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2021-08-03",
    "date": "2021-10-04T14:29:35Z",
    "text": "Restore Everyone's Sleep Tonight Act of 2021 or the REST Act of 2021\n\nThis bill authorizes an airport to impose an access restriction between the hours of 10 p.m. and 7 a.m. for aircrafts.\n\nAn airport may impose a noise deterrence penalty on an air carrier or aircraft operator for a violation of the access restriction.\n\nThe restriction does not apply to the operation of military, law enforcement, and U.S. Coast Guard flights."
  },
